<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="535" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,945,1223]" pageId="12" pageNumber="535">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,1160,1187]" pageId="12" pageNumber="535">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Fifth antennomere with dense tuft of setae; lower ocular lobe as tall as genae; elytra with centrobasal crest, without longitudinal carina. Number of species currently included: 12.
